snippet.title: Another Crab's Treasure | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
WE DID IT. WE LAUNCHED. FR FR WE ACTUALLY DID IT. 

Another Crab's Treasure is now out on Nintendo Switch, Xbox Game Pass, Steam and PS5! If you haven't grabbed it already what are you still doing here??? Finish the trailer and hit the tide pools bro. 

To be totally cringe and cute thank you for all the love and support on this journey these past few years. We couldn't have done it without you xoxo 

IT'S TIME FOR CRAB.

Video Production + Additional Sounds: 
Paige Wilson

Animated Segment:
David Liu
Brandon Frasier
Quinn Taketa

"Grovekeeper Topoda" Song: 
Fe

Sound Design and Scoring: 
Avery Winter McFarland

Special Thanks: 
Midas Klare
